        <Node ToolID="98">
          <GuiSettings Plugin="AlteryxGuiToolkit.TextBox.TextBox">
            <Position x="66" y="639" width="493" height="206" />
          </GuiSettings>
          <Properties>
            <Configuration>
              <Text>- Use the Input tool to bring in a Customer file with purchase data. 

- Use the Create Points tool to assign a spatial object to each customer row based on the latitude and longitude columns.

- Use a second Input tool to bring in ZIP Code file.

- Use the Spatial Match tool to assign a spatial relationship where a customer is within a ZIP Code.

- Use the Summarize tool to determine a customer purchase total per ZIP Code.

- Use the Formula tool to create a new column to label the ZIP Codes on the map. The total purchase is converted to a string, a "$" is appended and the appropriate comma is included.</Text>
              <Font name="Segoe UI" size="8.25" style="0" />
              <TextColor name="Black" />
              <FillColor name="White" />
              <Shape shape="3" />
              <Justification Justification="0" />
            </Configuration>
            <Annotation DisplayMode="0">
              <Name />
              <DefaultAnnotationText />
              <Left value="False" />
            </Annotation>
          </Properties>
